## 👔Projects

### Shopee clone

This is a project to clone the user page of the e-commerce platform [Shopee](https://shopee.com).

**Technologies used**: REST API, ReactJs, Typescript, Tailwindcss, React Router, React Hook Form, Yup, React Query, Webpack, ESLint, Prettier, React Helmet

**Functions include**:

- Manage authentication with JWT (automatic token refresh applied)
- Use the Yup and React Hook Form to validate the form.
- Smart Pagination, Filter, and Product Search
- Incorporate state into the URL to easily share results across devices.
- Asynchronous state management with React Query
- Code Splitting
- Improve performance by optimizing build file size analysis.
- SEO with React Helmet
- Separate the private and public routes.

**🔗Webiste**: [Frontend-ShoppeClone-Typescript](https://frontend-shoppe-clone-typescript.vercel.app)

**🔐Account for testing**: `Admin+1@gmail.com` / `123123`

**🔗Github**: [Frontend-ShoppeClone-Typescript](https://github.com/Phucndh1610/Frontend-ShoppeClone-Typescript)

### Movie

This is a movie ticket booking project, which I designed and coded myself.

**Technologies used**: ReactJs, Create React App, React Router, Redux, Antd, REST API, Yup

**Functions include**:

- Book tickets, ticket management, seat management, product Search
- Use the Yup validate the form.
- Fully responsive website
- Scoped CSS with Styled Component
- React Redux is used to manage state.
- Code Splitting

**🔗Webiste**: [Movie](https://cybersoft-movie-hongphuc.vercel.app)

**🔗Github**: [Frontend-Movie](https://github.com/Phucndh1610/DuAnTotNghiep_BCDN01_Movie_ReactJs)

